short_summary: TBIPS (Task-Based Informatics Professional Services) - Request for Proposal
description: The contract is for professional services of consulting for FCAC, including but not limited to application development, business analysis, and project management. The contract is for a period of time, not specified, at a rate of $ per hour/minute.
